      <title>摩根大通称套利交易的解体尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/unraveling-of-carry-trade-not-done-yet-jpmorgan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通全球外汇策略联席主管 Arindam Sandilya 表示：“至少在投机投资界，套利交易平仓已经完成 50%-60%。”他在彭博电视上发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/unraveling-of-carry-trade-not-done-yet-jpmorgan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:20:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
